 to resolve any issues should this arise.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Inclement Weather<\/strong><br \/>\u2013 In the event of inclement weather you must assume the group will go ahead unless you hear otherwise from us.<br \/>\u2013 Any sessions cancelled by us prior to the start time will be made up at another time of our choosing. Every effort will be made to put the make up session on a date and time that suits the majority where possible.<br \/>\u2013 Once a session has started it is deemed to have taken place and will not be made up if the weather turns bad during the session.<br \/>\u2013 The coach may leave the club after 15 minutes passed the start time if nobody shows and has not been warned of your late arrival.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Course Cancellation\/Refunds<\/strong><br \/>\u2013 No refunds will be issued once enrolled onto a course.<br \/>\u2013 If you miss a session you may ask permission to make it up in another group that term providing there is another group on offer that is of a suitable level and there is sufficient space to accommodate any extra persons. If you wish to do this you MUST confirm with us.<br \/>\u2013 Any courses that have insufficient numbers of participants may be cancelled at our discretion.<br \/>\u2013 If a session is cancelled by us due to coach unavailability we will make up that session during the week following the last week of the course.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Administration Fee<\/strong><br \/>\u2013 An administration fee may be applied to transactions or changes requested by the customer. One example could be where uPlay Sports would incur a bank or credit card fee.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Membership and group pricing at HBS LTC<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u2013 The block-booking price is only available to members of HBS LTC.<br \/>\u2013 Non-members are permitted to attend sessions for a maximum of 3 sessions, after which they must join as a member to continue.<br \/>\u2013 Membership is not required for Tots Tennis session attendees.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; module_id=&#8221;direct-debit-coaching-plan&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Direct Debit Coaching Plan \u2013 Tennis Groups at Hitchin Boys School Lawn Tennis Club and Biggleswade Tennis Club<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><em>Please ensure you have fully read and understood the terms and conditions<\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong><u>How to Set-up your Direct Debit<\/u><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Simply email office@uplaysports.co.uk\u00a0stating the participant name, group name and day you would like to attend and that you would like to sign up to the direct debit system.<\/li>\n<li>You will then receive an email from GoCardless asking you to authorise uPlay Sports to set up your direct debit.<\/li>\n<li>Click on the link in the email and fill out the form and you\u2019re done!<\/li>\n<li>The Direct Debit is now set up and you are protected by the Direct Debit guarantee as always!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Hitchin Boys School Lawn Tennis Club<\/h4>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-1\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-1\">\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">Term<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">Cost per Term<br \/>\nRed, Orange, Green &amp; Yellow Groups<br \/>\nMixed Coaching 1 &amp; Rusty Rackets<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">Cost per Term<br \/>\nTots Tennis<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">Cost per Term Mixed Coaching 2 &amp; Monday Drills<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\"><\/td><td class=\"column-2\"><\/td><td class=\"column-3\"><\/td><td class=\"column-4\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">Spring Term 2020<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">\u00a3102.00<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">\u00a384.00<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">\u00a3138.00<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">Summer Term 2020<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">\u00a3102.00<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">\u00a384.00<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">\u0